INSTALLATION STEPS

STEP 1 :
- Install the Dependences of MA-SOCRATIS

STEP 2:
- Install  MA-SOCRATIS main core

  cd /to_src

  mkdir build

  cd build

  cmake ..

  make install .

  cmake ..

STEP 2:

- RUN your simulation

  cd ../test

  ./auto_segm ../Atlas.cfg 

STEP 3:

- ENJOY ;)






TIP:

MANUALLY INSTALLATION OF PYTHON DL CODE

- If there is an issue with the python code then try to install the Initial segmentation code manually by:
  
  cd ../Initial_Segmentation

  pip install .

  cd keras-contrib-master

  pip install .

  cd ../deep-belief-network-master

  pip install .


